## Structural code context (Atelier-first)

Use Atelier MCP tools first for symbol and code-intel workflows. CodeGraph is fallback-only.

| Question | Preferred tool |
|---|---|
| "What files exist under path/" | `mcp__atelier__code op=files` |
| "Where is X defined?" / "Find symbol named X" | `mcp__atelier__code op=search` |
| "Show me Y's signature/source" | `mcp__atelier__code op=node` |
| "What calls function Y?" | `mcp__atelier__code op=callers` |
| "What does Y call?" | `mcp__atelier__code op=callees` |
| "What breaks if I change Z?" | `mcp__atelier__code op=impact` |
| "Give me focused context for task T" | `mcp__atelier__code op=context` |
| "Show related symbols + code together" | `mcp__atelier__code op=explore` |

Use `codegraph_*` only when an Atelier code-intel op is unavailable or returns `noop`.
<!-- CODEGRAPH_END -->
